**Spiritualist** | Townsfolk Power | Haunted
__Basics__
Once the Spiritualist becomes a ghost, they can whisper to a living player each night.
__Details__
Each night, if they are a ghost, the Spiritualist may select a player. From the moment of selection until the end of the following day, the Spiritualist may anonymously whisper with their target.
The Spiritualist may only pick each target once. Selecting a player is an immediate ability.

__Simplified__
After the Spiritualist dies, they can whisper to one player each night.

__Formalized__
Ghostly Role
Immediate Night: [Attribute: @Selection lacks `SpiritTouched`] {Direct} |spiritualist.1|
  • Conversation Reset `Spirit Touched`
  • Grant `Spirit Touched` to @Selection
  • Whisper to `Spirit Touched` as `Spiritualist` (~NextDay)
  • Apply `SpiritTouched` to @Selection
Passive Start Night: Conversation Reset `Spirit Touched`

__Card__
The Spiritualist can whisper to the living while dead.
